{"data":[{"name":"104:1","price":"(1) Woe to every scorner and mocker","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6180,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:2","price":"(2) Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it.[1987]","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6181,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1987]- Rather than spending in the way of Allāh.","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:3","price":"(3) He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal.","arabic":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6182,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:4","price":"(4) No! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher.[1988]","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6183,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1988]- i.e., Hellfire, which crushes and destroys all that enters it.","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:5","price":"(5) And what can make you know what is the Crusher?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6184,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:6","price":"(6) It is the fire of Allāh, [eternally] fueled,","arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6185,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:7","price":"(7) Which mounts directed at the hearts.[1989]","arabic":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6186,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1989]- Covering them and penetrating them.","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:8","price":"(8) Indeed, it [i.e., Hellfire] will be closed down upon them","arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6187,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"104:9","price":"(9) In extended columns.[1990]","arabic":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6188,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1990]- Interpreted to be either columns of fire or columns of iron to which are chained the inmates of Hell.","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah","Chapter Al-Humazah","Humazah","Surah Humazah","Chapter Humazah","Al Humazah","Surah Al Humazah","Chapter Al Humazah","Surah 104","Chapter 104","The Traducer","الهمزة"]}